                "name": "6B47 Ratnik-BSh upgraded helmet (EMR cover)",
                "shortName": "6B47-U EMR",
                "description": "An upgraded 6B47 Ratnik-BSh helmet with an EMR Digital Flora cover. Originally developed as a lightweight aramid helmet for the Ratnik program, this modified version has been reinforced with additional ballistic material and improved internal padding. The upgrade increases protection to Class 5 while retaining standard mounting equipment for lights and night vision devices. Heavier than the original, but much better suited for serious work."
